{"id": 3111, "genre": 1001, "title": "掉血的时候，你都有哪些不太一样的精神自救法？", "description": "你的心情自救手册里都有哪些特别条例？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock ）", "record_count": 950, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200102205602uBCixnyNsdahUZqR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-02T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 351490, "content": "看海", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693133}, {"id": 351492, "content": "恋与制作人（四个野男人）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461775}, {"id": 351496, "content": "玩游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675484}, {"id": 351497, "content": "一个人去吃海底捞", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659624}, {"id": 351499, "content": "努力让自己更悲伤，悲伤到极致，反而自愈了。", "image": "img/option/option/20200105180609d6xvKVfr2bgyliRm.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674870}, {"id": 351501, "content": "向神皇祷告。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676457}, {"id": 351502, "content": "背诵巨魔语录\n我们遇到什么困难也不要怕 微笑的面对他 消除恐惧的最好办法就是面对恐惧 坚持才是胜利。奥利给", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676457}, {"id": 351504, "content": "我是谁？我在做什么？我在哪儿？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289185}, {"id": 351517, "content": "上帝视角环视周围，各做各事，并没有人注意自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1610340}, {"id": 351519, "content": "想想以前血槽空的时候，然后自我安慰都会过去的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282904}, {"id": 351775, "content": "做手工，车个包就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921335}, {"id": 351520, "content": "原本我以为掉血是指姨妈造访，点进来一看怎么有这么多男士回答！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026193}, {"id": 351524, "content": "看脱口秀和治愈动画 比如《妖精森林的小不点》", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 351532, "content": "《当下的力量》，《禅的初心》，《苦才是人生》，《坎贝尔生活美学》…都是值得反复阅读给人持续带来力量的好书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 351538, "content": "走街串巷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640904}, {"id": 351800, "content": "看一些悲剧和凄惨结局的小说，你看他们比我还惨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534156}, {"id": 352322, "content": "沉默思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 351813, "content": "看喜欢的up主的学习视频，十分钟后又充满了动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223289}, {"id": 351567, "content": "吃，看点喜欢的视频，睡一觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 352607, "content": "流血了，再来一道，深刻铭记。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630544}, {"id": 351588, "content": "我还能再抢救下..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676655}, {"id": 351595, "content": "仰观宇宙之大，俯察品类之盛。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659562}, {"id": 351612, "content": "搞黄", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676748}, {"id": 352642, "content": "戴上耳机，骑上共享单车在学校的晚上没有目的骑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693490}, {"id": 351370, "content": "做汇报／演讲之前看看宇宙纪录片，紧张个屁，人类算个啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 244, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351371, "content": "去墓园逛一圈读读墓志铭就会平静下来，人人死而平等", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351372, "content": "收藏一个“打鸡血”歌单，不想做事的时候听完干劲＋1", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351373, "content": "感觉颓废就去一趟宜家，会更热爱生活一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351376, "content": "吃。别不独特，也不算健康，但真的很爽且充满希望。", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256134}, {"id": 351378, "content": "一个人逛超市吧，看到别人成对或者一家人在一起的就觉得他们努力生活经营的样子很美好很幸福，自己也从他们那里偷来了一丝快乐和生活气息，然后就也买点东西快乐吃喝辽。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272453}, {"id": 351379, "content": "去公园跑上十公里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334072}, {"id": 351380, "content": "仰望星空，如果还能看到星星的话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044540}, {"id": 351382, "content": "看一场喜欢的电影，看治愈系日剧，买一杯咖啡，去公园散步，看有趣的真人秀，比如粉雄救兵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140282}, {"id": 351383, "content": "在b站看生活类vlog 觉得生活可以自己经营得更加精致", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72077}, {"id": 351384, "content": "喝加糖的咖啡或奶茶……刷爱豆的视频……一个拯救我的身体一个支撑我的精神……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533703}, {"id": 351385, "content": "磕cp", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506800}, {"id": 351387, "content": "按压止血，然后去医院", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912804}, {"id": 351388, "content": "看悲伤的电影，如果可以，默默地流一点眼泪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1548241}, {"id": 351389, "content": "疯狂健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453774}, {"id": 351390, "content": "把事情梳理一遍，写下来，通过文字记录整理就能把事情想通了。如果记录之后还是觉得无法止血，那就是理不顺，解决不了的事情，既然无可奈何，那就算了吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054564}, {"id": 351391, "content": "看看爱豆的照片和现场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460097}, {"id": 351392, "content": "撸", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639703}, {"id": 351393, "content": "逛超市，逛菜市场，自己煮一顿饭，边看能让人笑出声的综艺边吃饭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223736}, {"id": 351394, "content": "要运动吧  一定要运动\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430398}, {"id": 351395, "content": "血槽快空的时候，扇自己几巴掌：冷静点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131816}, {"id": 351396, "content": "直面", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 351397, "content": "看老友记", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460417}, {"id": 351654, "content": "看小说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662943}, {"id": 351399, "content": "深呼吸，喊两下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247392}, {"id": 351655, "content": "猛踩油门", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734353}]}